      "acceptanceCriteria": "Equivalency between validation experiment input parameters and COU input parameters must be formally demonstrated with quantified similarity metrics.",
      "rationale": "Factor not assessed; equivalency mapping between bench experiment and VAD COU inputs has not been performed. Epistemic gap documented at MRL 5."
